channel.title: [PI] Engine load?
channel.description:
okay so this is my first rsps and im new to java (been learning as i go for a month or so :P) im using sagi x evolution as a base and have made quite a lot of changes however i recently noticed the engine load with about 11 players on is at 20% this is while on a vps too, im not totally sure what the engine load actually is i know that the higher it is the more lagg there will be however im not totally sure of what factors effect it, if someone could explain this to me and possibly show me how i can fix this i would be extremely greatful
thanks :) chris
